Package: BayesRS
Type: Package
Title: Bayes Factors for Hierarchical Linear Models with Continuous Predictors
Version: 0.1.2
Authors@R: c(person(given="Mirko", family="Thalmann", role=c("aut", "cre"),
             email="mirkothalmann@hotmail.com"), person(given="Marcel",
             family="Niklaus", role="aut"), person(given="Klaus",
             family="Oberauer", role="ths"),person(given="John",
             family="Kruschke", role="ctb"))
Depends: 
	R (>= 3.0.0)
Imports:
    rjags,
    ggplot2,
    metRology,
    grid,
    reshape,
    methods,
    coda
Description: Runs hierarchical linear Bayesian models. Samples from the posterior
    distributions of model parameters in JAGS (Just Another Gibbs Sampler; Plummer, 2003, <https://www.r-project.org/conferences/DSC-2003/Proceedings/Plummer.pdf>). Computes Bayes factors for group 
    parameters of interest with the Savage-Dickey density ratio (Wetzels, Raaijmakers, Jakab, Wagenmakers, 2009, <doi:10.3758/PBR.16.4.752>).
